OL,3,CPep Guardiola apologises for 'I want
OL,4,Cto harm myself' comment
OL,6,FManchester City manager Pep Guardiola
OL,7,Fhas apologised after saying "I want to
OL,8,Fharm myself" when asked about why his
OL,9,Fface was covered in scratches -
OL,10,Finsisting he did not mean to make
OL,11,Flight of self harm.
OL,13,FThe Spaniard was spotted with red
OL,14,Fmarks on his face and head after he
OL,15,Fsaw his his team concede three goals
OL,16,Fin last 15 minutes of their Champions
OL,17,FLeague game against Feyenoord to draw
OL,18,Fthree all.
