OL,3,CPep Guardiola apologises for 'I want
OL,4,Cto harm myself' comment
OL,6,FWhen asked about the marks, including
OL,7,Fa scratch on his nose, during his post-
OL,8,Fmatch conference Guardiola replied he
OL,9,Fhad caused it with a fingernail,
OL,10,Fadding apparently as a joke: "I want
OL,11,Fto harm myself."
OL,13,FBut, following backlash about the
OL,14,Fcomments, the City boss took to the
OL,15,Fsocial media site X to clarify his
OL,16,Fresponse.
