OL,3,CPep Guardiola apologises for 'I want
OL,4,Cto harm myself' comment
OL,6,FGuardiola said: "I was caught off
OL,7,Fguard with a question at the end of a
OL,8,Fpress conference last night about a
OL,9,Fscratch which had appeared on my face
OL,10,Fand explained that a sharp fingernail
OL,11,Fhad accidentally caused this.
OL,13,F"My answer was in no way intended to
OL,14,Fmake light of the very serious issue
OL,15,Fof self harm.
