OL,6,F"I know that many people struggle with
OL,7,Fmental health issues every day, and I
OL,8,Fwould like to take this moment to
OL,9,Fhighlight one of the ways in people
OL,10,Fcan seek help, by calling the
OL,11,FSamaritans hotline on 116 123 or
OL,12,Femailing jo@samaritans.org."
OL,14,FCity's losing run ended at the Etihad
OL,15,Fbut they conceded three times in the
OL,16,Ffinal 15 minutes on another
OL,17,Fdisappointing night and Guardiola held
OL,18,Fhis head in his hands in the dugout
OL,19,Fafter a Josko Gvardiol blunder gifted
OL,20,Fthe first Feyenoord goal to Anis Hadj
OL,21,FMoussa.
